title: How the Shoggoth Meme Has Come to Symbolize the State of A.I.
description: The Shoggoth, a character from a science fiction story, captures the essential weirdness of the A.I. moment.

title: Elizabeth Holmes Set to Report to Prison Tuesday in Texas
description: The disgraced founder of the blood testing start-up Theranos, who was convicted of fraud, is expected to report to a minimum-security prison in Texas.

title: A.I. Poses ‘Risk of Extinction,’ Industry Leaders Warn
description: Leaders from OpenAI, Google Deepmind, Anthropic and other A.I. labs warn that future systems could be as deadly as pandemics and nuclear weapons.

title: California Builds the Future, for Good and Bad. What’s Next?
description: From reparations to tax revolts, the Golden State tries out new ideas all the time. What roads will its latest experiments send us down?
